com.bitplan.mediawiki.japi.api

Packages that use com.bitplan.mediawiki.japi.api
com.bitplan.mediawiki.japi This library contains the classes that allow to connect to Mediawiki via a Java API. 
com.bitplan.mediawiki.japi.api This package contain the generated JAXB classes that allow to analyze the results returned by the Mediawiki API.
